name: O-liang The Dressing Room
description: My mother got me a paper doll when I was a kid, and I still enjoy playing it. I recall making a cartoon of a woman and designing an outfit for her to wear while playing. This resurfaced in my mind, so I created my Art in the style of a paper doll with my pets, with the intention of completing four rooms. The third is as follows: O-liang The Dressing Room.
